## Notes: In-game player toolkit for WoW Legends (WotLK 3.3.5a / AzerothCore) — build & command a party of AI bots, set their roles, run dungeons, tune your own XP rate, manage your personal Companion and opt into Hardcore. Sends only your own commands; needs no special permissions.
## Author: WoW Legends (timoinglin)
## Version: 0.1.0
